Description: A text that informs the player what keycard they need in order to open a locked door. "{0}" will be replaced by the ID of the keycard; do not alter these characters, just place them in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

Italian.Translation: Hai bisogno della chiave magnetica {0} per sbloccarla.

German.Translation: Sie benötigen die Schlüsselkarte {0} zum Entriegeln.

Spanish.Translation: Necesitas una tarjeta de acceso {0} para abrirla.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Você precisa do cartão de acesso {0} para abrir.

Japanese.Translation: 開錠にはキーカード {0} が必要。

name: InGame.InteractionPrompt.SecurityDoor.YouNeedKeycard_X
